s-4-7-introduces-new-theme-twenty-seventeen/">WordPress 4.7 introduces new theme: Twenty Seventeen</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://community.1and1.com">1&amp;1 Community</a>.</p>\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:32:"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/";a:1:{s:7:"creator";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:16:"Philipp Bellmann";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:40:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/";a:1:{s:7:"encoded";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:2383:"<p><a href="https://wordpress.org/news/2016/10/wordpress-4-7-beta-1/" target="_blank">WordPress 4.7</a> will be released in early December 2016. In addition to improvements and new features, 4.7 introduces a brand new theme: Twenty Seventeen. (Screenshots: wordpress.net)</p>\n<img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-10391" src="https://community.1und1.de/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/twenty-seventeen-overview.jpg" alt="twenty-seventeen-overview" width="2800" height="1800" />\n<p>Twenty Seventeen is optimized for business websites and brings your websites to life with an impressive video header, featured images, subtle animations, and multi-layered scrolling.</p>\n<img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-10393" src="https://community.1und1.de/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/twenty-seventeen-overview.gif" alt="twenty-seventeen-overview" width="864" height="540" />\n<p>Twenty Seventeen provides a flexible layout grid for the homepage, customizable widgets, navigation, logo and social menus.</p>\n<hr />\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a class="promo-button" href="http://2017.wordpress.net/" target="_blank">Twenty Seventeen Live-Demo</a></p>\n<h2 style="text-align: left;">Screenshots</h2>\n<img class="aligncenter wp-image-10389" src="https://community.1und1.de/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/wp-twenty-seventteen-start-video-header-1024x640.png" alt="wp-twenty-seventteen-start-video-header" width="640" height="400" />\n<hr />\n<img class="aligncenter wp-image-10388" src="https://community.1und1.de/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/wp-twenty-seventteen-start-parallax.png" alt="wp-twenty-seventteen-start-parallax" width="640" height="400" />\n<hr />\n<img class="aligncenter wp-image-10386" src="https://community.1und1.de/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/wp-twenty-seventteen-start-blog-overview.png" alt="wp-twenty-seventteen-start-blog-overview" width="640" height="400" />\n<hr />\n<img class="aligncenter wp-image-10385" src="https://community.1und1.de/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/wp-twenty-seventteen-blog-article-header-large.png" alt="wp-twenty-seventteen-blog-article-header-large" width="640" height="400" />\n<p>The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://community.1and1.com/wordpress-4-7-introduces-new-theme-twenty-seventeen/">WordPress 4.7 introduces new theme: Twenty Seventeen</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://community.1and1.com">1&amp;1 Community</a>.</p>\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:85:"https://community.1and1.com/wordpress-4-7-introduces-new-theme-twenty-seventeen/feed/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:38:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/";a:1:{s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1:"0";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:9;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:69:"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:5:{s:0:"";a:7:{s:5:"title";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:18:"Plesk Onyx preview";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"link";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4: