alse";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:11:"description";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:394:"<p>Plesk makes server administration easy. Admins and web developers can adjust settings, manage domains, call up statistics and install apps in one clearly laid out web interface.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://community.1and1.com/plesk-onyx-preview-cs/">Plesk Onyx preview</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://community.1and1.com">1&amp;1 Community</a>.</p>\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:32:"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/";a:1:{s:7:"creator";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:16:"Philipp Bellmann";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:40:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/";a:1:{s:7:"encoded";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:10418:"<p><strong>Plesk makes server administration easy. Admins and web developers can adjust settings, manage domains, call up statistics and install apps in one clearly laid out web interface.</strong></p>\n<iframe src="//www.youtube.com/embed/sIkE5MN2rwc" width="740" height="416" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen="allowfullscreen"></iframe>\n<p>Plesk Onyx is free for <a href="https://www.1and1.com/dynamic-cloud-server">1&amp;1 Cloud Server</a> and <a href="https://www.1and1.com/vps-hosting">1&amp;1 Virtual Server Cloud</a>.</p>\n<p>New in Plesk Onyx</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Plesk Onyx now comes with additional support for Git, in order to make website deployment even easier for developers.</li>\n<li>With Docker support, Docker containers can now be easily deployed and managed directly from the Plesk web interface.</li>\n<li>Support for the forthcoming Windows Server 2016 provides future security.</li>\n<li>System updates become easier with improved support of the yum and apt package managers.You can choose between manual and automatic updates and adjust the update settings for individual packages—all comfortably through the web interface.</li>\n<li>What&#8217;s more, Plesk Onyx offers support for DNSSEC and brings further improvements for SSL. For example, you can now enforce HTTPS connections to your Plesk-hosted websites to improve the security of your visitors.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Click on the <a href="https://docs.plesk.com/release-notes/17.0/whats-new/">Plesk Onyx release notes</a> to find out more about Plesk Onyx.</p>\n<h2>Plesk features</h2>\n<p>The most important features at a glance. Screenshots: <a href="https://www.plesk.com/">plesk.com</a></p>\n<h3><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-9538" src="https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/plesk-Features-I-Plesk.png" alt="plesk-features-i-plesk" width="2800" height="2882" srcset="https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/plesk-Features-I-Plesk.png 2800w, https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/plesk-Features-I-Plesk-291x300.png 291w, https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/plesk-Features-I-Plesk-768x790.png 768w, https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/plesk-Features-I-Plesk-995x1024.png 995w" sizes="(max-width: 2800px) 100vw, 2800px" /></h3>\n<h3>Websites and managing domains</h3>\n<img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-9549" src="https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/plesk-Websites-domains.png" alt="plesk-websites-domains" width="2800" height="1548" srcset="https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/plesk-Websites-domains.png 2800w, https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/plesk-Websites-domains-300x166.png 300w, https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/plesk-Websites-domains-768x425.png 768w, https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/plesk-Websites-domains-1024x566.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 2800px) 100vw, 2800px" />\n<p>Here you can find important settings for your websites and domains. For example, Manage FTP settings, e-mail, PHP versions, Apache and nginx settings or SSL configurations.</p>\n<h3>E-mail</h3>\n<img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-9548" src="https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/plesk-Mail-Plesk-Onyx-17.0.17.png" alt="plesk-mail-plesk-onyx-17-0-17" width="2800" height="1548" srcset="https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/plesk-Mail-Plesk-Onyx-17.0.17.png 2800w, https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/plesk-Mail-Plesk-Onyx-17.0.17-300x166.png 300w, https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/plesk-Mail-Plesk-Onyx-17.0.17-768x425.png 768w, https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/plesk-Mail-Plesk-Onyx-17.0.17-1024x566.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 2800px) 100vw, 2800px" />\n<p>Where would we be without e-mail? Set up your e-mail here.</p>\n<h3>Manage and install applications</h3>\n<img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-9547" src="https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/plesk-Plesk-managing-apps-onyx-17.0.17.png" alt="plesk-plesk-managing-apps-onyx-17-0-17" width="2800" height="1548" srcset="https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/plesk-Plesk-managing-apps-onyx-17.0.17.png 2800w, https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/plesk-Plesk-managing-apps-onyx-17.0.17-300x166.png 300w, https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/plesk-Plesk-managing-apps-onyx-17.0.17-768x425.png 768w, https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/plesk-Plesk-managing-apps-onyx-17.0.17-1024x566.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 2800px) 100vw, 2800px" />\n<p>Install and manage CMS easily. From big names to specialized apps, almost everything is available to you.</p>\n<img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-9540" src="https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/plesk-Plesk-managing-apps-install-onyx-17.0.17.png" alt="plesk-plesk-managing-apps-install-onyx-17-0-17" width="2800" height="1426" srcset="https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/plesk-Plesk-managing-apps-install-onyx-17.0.17.png 2800w, https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/plesk-Plesk-managing-apps-install-onyx-17.0.17-300x153.png 300w, https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/plesk-Plesk-managing-apps-install-onyx-17.0.17-768x391.png 768w, https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/plesk-Plesk-managing-apps-install-onyx-17.0.17-1024x522.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 2800px) 100vw, 2800px" />\n<p>Choose the desired software version before installation or adjust the installation according to your needs (custom version).</p>\n<h3>Create and manage databases</h3>\n<img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-9546" src="https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/plesk-Databases-for-demo.plesk_.com-Plesk-Onyx-17.0.17.png" alt="plesk-databases-for-demo-plesk-com-plesk-onyx-17-0-17" width="2800" height="1600" srcset="https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/plesk-Databases-for-demo.plesk_.com-Plesk-Onyx-17.0.17.png 2800w, https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/plesk-Databases-for-demo.plesk_.com-Plesk-Onyx-17.0.17-300x171.png 300w, https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/plesk-Databases-for-demo.plesk_.com-Plesk-Onyx-17.0.17-768x439.png 768w, https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/plesk-Databases-for-demo.plesk_.com-Plesk-Onyx-17.0.17-1024x585.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 2800px) 100vw, 2800px" />\n<p>Everything you need for your data bases: edit databases with phpMyAdmin, create and import database dumps. Manage database users. Set up database servers. Create backups.</p>\n<h3>Call up statistics</h3>\n<img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-9545" src="https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/plesk-Statistics-for-demo.plesk_.com-Plesk-Onyx-17.0.17.png" alt="plesk-statistics-for-demo-plesk-com-plesk-onyx-17-0-17" width="2800" height="1296" srcset="https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/plesk-Statistics-for-demo.plesk_.com-Plesk-Onyx-17.0.17.png 2800w, https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/plesk-Statistics-for-demo.plesk_.com-Plesk-Onyx-17.0.17-300x139.png 300w, https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/plesk-Statistics-for-demo.plesk_.com-Plesk-Onyx-17.0.17-768x355.png 768w, https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/plesk-Statistics-for-demo.plesk_.com-Plesk-Onyx-17.0.17-1024x474.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 2800px) 100vw, 2800px" />\n<p>Storage space, traffic, utilization according to service—here you can keep track with detailed statistics.</p>\n<h3>Tools and settings</h3>\n<img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-9544" src="https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/plesk-Tools-settings.png" alt="plesk-tools-settings" width="2800" height="1606" srcset="https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/plesk-Tools-settings.png 2800w, https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/plesk-Tools-settings-300x172.png 300w, https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/plesk-Tools-settings-768x441.png 768w, https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/plesk-Tools-settings-1024x587.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 2800px) 100vw, 2800px" />\n<p>All the settings an admin&#8217;s heart desires—in one place.</p>\n<h3>Manage and install extensions</h3>\n<img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-9543" src="https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/plesk-Extensions-Management-Plesk-Onyx-17.0.17.png" alt="plesk-extensions-management-plesk-onyx-17-0-17" width="2800" height="1292" srcset="https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/plesk-Extensions-Management-Plesk-Onyx-17.0.17.png 2800w, https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/plesk-Extensions-Management-Plesk-Onyx-17.0.17-300x138.png 300w, https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/plesk-Extensions-Management-Plesk-Onyx-17.0.17-768x354.png 768w, https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/plesk-Extensions-Management-Plesk-Onyx-17.0.17-1024x473.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 2800px) 100vw, 2800px" />\n<p>Upload, manage and install extensions from the catalogue.</p>\n<h3>Manage users / rights</h3>\n<img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-9542" src="https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/plesk-My-Profile-Plesk-Onyx-17.0.17.png" alt="plesk-my-profile-plesk-onyx-17-0-17" width="2800" height="1292" srcset="https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/plesk-My-Profile-Plesk-Onyx-17.0.17.png 2800w, https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/plesk-My-Profile-Plesk-Onyx-17.0.17-300x138.png 300w, https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/plesk-My-Profile-Plesk-Onyx-17.0.17-768x354.png 768w, https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/plesk-My-Profile-Plesk-Onyx-17.0.17-1024x473.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 2800px) 100vw, 2800px" />\n<p>Adjust user settings, generate passwords and set interface languages.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a class="promo-button" href="http://plesk.com/">Plesk Onyx demo (plesk.com)</a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://community.1and1.com/plesk-onyx-preview-cs/">Plesk Onyx preview</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://community.1and1.com">1&amp;1 Community</a>.</p>\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:55:"https://community.1and1.com/plesk-onyx-preview-cs/feed/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:38:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/";a:1:{s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1:"0";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}}}s:27:"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom";a:1:{s:4:"link";a:1:{i:0;a: